{"tid":180101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家可唔可以討論一下咩叫愛？","createTime":"2017-03-30T16:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T04:33:54.000Z","uid":60319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"353de2a1681275e82080f76868b760ad1aac288f","tid":180101,"uid":60319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:48:17.000Z","msg":"我愛上左個女仔<br />\n佢同我講佢根本唔知咩叫愛<br />\n我點答佢。<br />\n佢話佢鐘意我<br />\n但從來未愛過人<br />\n因為佢唔知咩叫愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好痛苦<br />\n<br />\n有冇人答到我<br />\n我覺得愛就係好care一個人<br />\n做咩都會受到佢影響<br />\n會好在意對方感受之類"},{"pid":"8707a1803b07dd83dbfa18b1040b20333d94e4a1","tid":180101,"uid":4210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:49:38.000Z","msg":"肯為個人付出"},{"pid":"d5f244c389bdf09e41fb28a2987ba8750a5e2013","tid":180101,"uid":15112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"其實我都係咁諗<br />\n會為愛既人著想 會想佢開心<br />\n可惜我慢慢覺得我男朋友只係鍾意我 而唔係愛我"},{"pid":"673848be9207fdb093dc2bd1d45ad22eaf787c17","tid":180101,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我都係咁諗<br />\n會為愛既人著想 會想佢開心<br />\n可惜我慢慢覺得我男朋友只係鍾意我 而唔係愛我</blockquote><br />\nGay"},{"pid":"3bb3c28eeba38760adb7e10b6964163bd3960cfc","tid":180101,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"會照顧嗰個人感受（比起平時你講野唔hurt到人嗰種會更加從嗰個人角度出發）<br />\n願意為對方付出 盡你能力俾最好嘅佢<br />\n包容接納體諒 <br />\n關注對方嘅情緒 同埋被佢嘅情緒牽動"},{"pid":"2a99cf4829609844f6cdc082693a1656539880e2","tid":180101,"uid":56627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:58:31.000Z","msg":"肯被你中出"},{"pid":"f4713a2feda02c88904af5829274227a1490cb0e","tid":180101,"uid":85537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"做愛"},{"pid":"a70c87b564b30512820d3cb93346a60fcedcb19b","tid":180101,"uid":60319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim